      <title>乌克兰腐败官员盗走4000万美元用于购买俄罗斯战争武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/ukraine-says-corrupt-officials-stole-40-million-meant-to-buy-arms-for-the-war-with-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰基辅（美联社）——据乌克兰安全部门报道，乌克兰一家军火公司的员工与国防部官员合谋挪用了近 4000 万美元，专门用于购买 10 万枚迫击炮弹，用于对俄战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/ukraine-says-corrupt-officials-stole-40-million-meant-to-buy-arms-for-the-war-with-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国上诉法院批准诺贝尔奖获得者穆罕默德·尤努斯保释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/bangladesh-appeals-court-grants-bail-to-nobel-laureate-muhammad-yunus-in-labor-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国达卡（美联社）——孟加拉国一家上诉法院周日批准诺贝尔奖获得者穆罕默德·尤努斯保释，他早些时候因违反该国劳动法而被判处六个月监禁。法院还同意听取针对他的判决的上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/bangladesh-appeals-court-grants-bail-to-nobel-laureate-muhammad-yunus-in-labor-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国秘书长在工作人员遭受袭击后敦促支持加沙工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/un-head-urges-support-for-gaza-work-after-staff-blamed-in-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国秘书长发誓将对加沙任何参与十月份袭击以色列的人员采取果断行动，同时敦促各国不要在战争仍在继续时停止向接受援助的“绝望民众”提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/un-head-urges-support-for-gaza-work-after-staff-blamed-in-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 07:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
